## Benchmark pack direction

- Aim Brain must not be Voltaic-only.
- Voltaic, Viscose, Custom, and future benchmarks should be separate benchmark packs.
- The universal engine handles raw runs, stats, trends, consistency, weakness detection, recommendations, and coach summaries.
- Benchmark packs provide scenarios, ranks, thresholds, native categories, universal category mapping, supported platforms, version metadata, and source notes.
- If threshold data is missing, return progress-only mode. Never invent ranks.

